title: Annie Lederman
itunes:title: Annie Lederman
description:
Comedian Annie Lederman is back!  In this episode she and Whitney investigate squirting and talk about dating younger men.  Annie also tells us about her beef with the band Train and signing ball sacs on tour.  Annie's podcast TRASH TUESDAY comes out every Tuesday https://www.youtube.com/c/TrashTuesday and go to https://www.annielederman.com/ for tour dates.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
